'''''Atlas''''' group was a group of [[Heavy Lifter/Legends|Heavy Lifter]] transports dedicated solely to the Rebel Alliance. They were primarily used to pick up captured Imperial cargo. At one point it was responsible for stealing new fighters from the new [[TIE Experimental Project]].

